snippet.title: LAURA BENANTI AND CHAD HODGE TALK AMBER HEARD - 2/10/13 - THE DINNER PARTY SHOW
snippet.description:
While live on the air with THE DINNER PARTY SHOW hosts, CHRISTOPHER RICE and ERIC SHAW QUINN, Tony winner LAURA BENANTI and hot T.V writer CHAD HODGE discuss a special game they used to play on the set of NBC's THE PLAYBOY CLUB called "What Would Amber Do?" (Amber being the gorgeous and talented AMBER HEARD)

(We're always on! A new live cast of THE DINNER PARTY SHOW debuts every Sunday evening at 8 PM ET/ 5 PM PT at www.TheDinnerPartyShow.com, followed by continuous encore performances. You can also listen in via our FREE MOBILE APPS for Apple and Android devices, and our iTunes podcast features the entire show.)
